column5: Can anyone tell me from experience of what fish speicies are in this lake?? Doing some research,,,saying that there is only musky and largemouth bass,,,can it be only these two speicies in this lake??  Is there a site the details spiecies in each lake?

I've fished Kahshe a number of times, there are also pike, smallmouth, and walleye.  You might be able to find out more about the species if you find the Guide To Eating Sportfish. Will tell you how clean the water is if you want to keep fish but will also tell you what species are present.  Mike
Sonny try this link it is last years tournament winners on the lake. http://www.kahshelake.ca/kids/fishing_2006.html  It ahs species and sizes of fish.  Easton
I have also heard there are crappie in there.  Joey
